{"tid":1994035,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(走，咱們上大陸復工) 德勤：中国下半年經濟將強勁復蘇","createTime":"2020-04-29T07:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T08:12:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4500232e00faa51c2e31abc0b376b77033c9a02","tid":1994035,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"德勤預期，中國第二季經濟增長將會持平，隨著產能利用率逐步恢復正常，經濟刺激措施發揮效用，中國經濟將在下半年强勁復蘇，將帶動香港及台灣地區、南韓及新加坡進口需求持續增長。<br />\n<br />\n德勤中國首席經濟學家許思濤表示，中國將不會再出現「大水漫灌式」強刺激政策。相反，政府對經濟刺激很可能將集中於新技術基礎設施投資、家庭消費以及具針對性的信貸寬鬆等方面。隨著這種財政刺激措施預計不久後陸續推出，有望拉動全年經濟增長超過3%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，德勤認為，由於香港對內地遊客高度依賴，以及與美元掛勾的匯率制度，經濟預計將出現大幅收縮。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523414-20200429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523414-20200429.htm&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=611a8276\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523414-20200429.htm&h=1ac0e51d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523414-20200429.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4ecdf456140adf9011a28aca9e5f735b77bc98dd","tid":1994035,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"是日關鍵字：渾水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b883bfe68d848af79a5ccb79c438e9dc2b25483","tid":1994035,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"德勤又退任核數師 逾4個月累涉46企<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200423/photo/bkn-20200423173224587-0423_00842_001_02b.jpg?20200423235829\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200423%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200423173224587-0423_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20200423235829&h=4bfccc43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on